            <div type="transcript" id="J1347">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Escape is such a thankful Word</l>
                    <l>I often in the Night</l>
                    <l>Consider it unto myself</l>
                    <l>No <app type="revision"><lem>Monster</lem><rdg>Monster</rdg></app>
spectacle in sight</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Escape -- it is the Basket</l>
                    <l>In which the Heart is caught</l>
                    <l>When down some awful Battlement</l>
                    <l>The rest of Life is dropt --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>'Tis not to sight the savior --</l>
                    <l>It is to be the saved --</l>
                    <l>And that is why I lay my Head</l>
                    <l>Upon this trusty word --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l></l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
